name: Watershed
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Head outdoors!
amenities.description: Head outdoors! Watershed neighbors the protected Patuxent Wildlife Refuge. Spend time exploring 13,000 acres of nature and wildlife.

amenities.name: Watershed residents
amenities.description: Watershed residents will have a convenient commute! Watershed is located close to the BW Parkway and Patuxent Freeway.

amenities.name: new homes
amenities.description: The new homes at Watershed are located close to major employers such as Fort Meade, NSA , and the National Business Park.

amenities.name: Watershed features
amenities.description: Watershed features an outdoor pool, bike park, and scenic trails.

amenities.name: Refuge clubhouse
amenities.description: The Refuge clubhouse features a yoga room, workout room, event room, co-working space, and lounge

amenities.name: Watershed features
amenities.description: Watershed features dynamic playscapes and gathering places for children

amenities.name: Enjoy nearby
amenities.description: Enjoy nearby Target and Kohl's as well as Total Wine, a Starbucks drive-thru, Panera, Chick-Fil-A, Chipotle and Sweet Frog!

amenities.name: Watershed located
amenities.description: Watershed is located just eleven miles from BWI Airport.

amenities.name: Laurel Town
amenities.description: Laurel Town Centre is 5 miles from Watershed and features a Harris Teeter, Outback Steakhouse, BJs Brewhouse, First Watch, Regal Movie Theater, and more.

amenities.name: Take kids
amenities.description: Take the kids to Dinosaur Park for the day, it's about 6 miles from Watershed.

amenities.name: This community
amenities.description: This community includes a Fiber network that provides fast, reliable, multi-user Internet needed in homes today and in the future.

amenities.name: Watershed only
amenities.description: Watershed is only about 2 miles from the Maryland City at Russett Library.

amenities.name: Watershed located
amenities.description: Watershed is located near the Eisenhower Golf Course and Renditions Golf Course.
